name: Network
description: Surrealistrasyon//Şerif Gümüşbaş//Digital Art//2000x2700 pixel//Like our blood veins and neural networks in our body, wires continue to make the whole world a part of a whole//Drawing is an impressive form of expression for me with its universal and differentiating structure for each viewer. And I like to use automatism as a tool to transfer the impressions I have gained while continuing to research and learn in many disciplines. Because I think this method is a symbolic, mysterious and striking way of expressing.
